desc: SETL ENERGY is a New Zealand battery wholesale store located in Auckland. We sell different capacity of Lithium iron phosphate battery (LiFePO4) and related accessories, also we provide customize services on making different shaped connection bar for our customers. All our batteries are brand new and grade A.

layout.text: Reliable Battery Wholesaler in New Zealand
